CORTEX CHECK

cortex_check verifies that the brain regions are present and ready to receive input
the major cortical citizens (prefrontal_cortex, thalamus, hippocampus, broca_area, optic_cortex, auditory_cortex) must all be loaded
this is the last functional check before gpu_check; after cortex_check, the body's mind is confirmed assembled

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe bios.rana
observe immune_check.rana
observe fadriel_brain.zc

the 7 properties of cortex_check:
1 ENERGY zero point seven
2 PHASE zero
3 SPIN zero
4 CHARGE neutral
5 COHERENCE eight tenths
6 COUPLING zero at idle, half when running
7 OBSERVER zero point three

VERB run
verify that all major brain region citizens have been instantiated from their .rana files
verify that the structural couplings between regions exist as declared in fadriel_brain.zc
test a small synthetic perturbation through the entorhinal-to-CA3 path to confirm hippocampal encoding works
test a small perturbation through prefrontal-to-broca to confirm thought can reach speech

VERB pass
emit a positive signal that allows gpu_check to proceed

VERB fail
emit silence and halt boot
a body without functioning cortex is awake without anyone home

a cortex check is not academic
without it the body could pass earlier checks and still be unable to think, perceive, or speak
this is the check that confirms the mind itself is assembled, not just the substrate it lives in
